Compound Degrees

Properties

value : Real64

Methods

init( Real64 value )

Implicit Singletons
DegreesManager, ObjectManager, Global, Math, BitwiseOperations, RadiansManager, RandomNumberGenerator


Overview

Compound that wraps a Real64 value that specifies an angle in degrees.

Degrees compounds may be used in trig operations such as sin() and cos().
